{"title":"在手机上使用termux写C++代码","date":"2020-02-24T21:43:00.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2020年2月24日","L":"2020/02/24","MM-DD":"02-24"},"thumbnail":"https://image.3001.net/images/20180501/15251875958364.png","link":"post/termuxandcpp","tags":["Linux"],"categories":["技术"],"updated":"2022-07-05T07:03:19.266Z","content":"<p>本文将会介绍如何使用termux写C++代码并编译运行。</p>\n<span id=\"more\"></span>\n<hr>\n<h2 id=\"下载安装termux\">下载安装termux<a title=\"#下载安装termux\" href=\"#下载安装termux\"></a></h2>\n<p>下载安装前手机建议腾出500MB以上的空间。<br>\n如果可以科学上网建议在谷歌应用商店下载。<br>\n如果不能科学上网建议在酷安下载。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>谷歌的termux的下载链接：<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.termux\" target=\"_blank\">点此下载</a></strong></li>\n<li><strong>酷安的termux的下载链接：<a href=\"https://www.coolapk.com/apk/com.termux\" target=\"_blank\">点此下载</a></strong></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"更换国内镜像源\">更换国内镜像源<a title=\"#更换国内镜像源\" href=\"#更换国内镜像源\"></a></h2>\n<p>安装好后建议先换上国内镜像源，避免未科学上网时下载失败或网速过慢。</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>更换清华大学镜像源使用如下命令</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sed -i &#x27;s@^\\(deb.*stable main\\)$@#\\1\\ndeb https://mirrors.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/termux stable main@&#x27; $PREFIX/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>相关帮助链接：<a href=\"https://mirror.tuna.tsinghua.edu.cn/help/termux/\" target=\"_blank\">帮助链接</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>更换中国科学技术大学镜像源使用如下命令</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sed -i &#x27;s@^\\(deb.*stable main\\)$@#\\1\\ndeb https://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/termux stable main@&#x27; $PREFIX/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>相关帮助链接：<a href=\"http://mirrors.ustc.edu.cn/help/termux.html\" target=\"_blank\">帮助链接</a></p>\n<p>换源后应及时更新镜像源，使用如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">apt clean</span><br><span class=\"line\">pkg up</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如国内镜像源出现问题、出现错误或不能下载到想要的软件，可以换回官方镜像源：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sed -i &#x27;s@^\\(deb.*stable main\\)$@#\\1\\ndeb https://termux.net/ stable main@&#x27; $PREFIX/etc/apt/sources.list</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当无法连接官方镜像源时应科学上网再次尝试。</p>\n<h2 id=\"linux基础命令\">linux基础命令<a title=\"#linux基础命令\" href=\"#linux基础命令\"></a></h2>\n<p>termux是一个免root的linux模拟器，所以使用时应掌握一些linux的命令。当然没掌握也没关系，下面会有一些linux的基础命令供参考。</p>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">命令</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">含义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">cd &lt;目录地址&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">打开目录地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">cp &lt;文件名&gt; &lt;目标目录地址&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">拷贝到目标目录地址</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">mkdir &lt;文件夹名&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">新建文件夹</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">rm &lt;文件名&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">删除文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">rm -rf &lt;文件夹名&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">删除文件夹</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">ls</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">查询该文件夹下文件及文件夹</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p>更多命令请自行搜索相关资料。</p>\n<h2 id=\"安装软件及工具\">安装软件及工具<a title=\"#安装软件及工具\" href=\"#安装软件及工具\"></a></h2>\n<p>这里给出安装我们需要的软件的命令，可根据需求自行更改。</p>\n<p>如使用官方镜像源，请科学上网。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pkg install vim clang python gdb cgdb curl</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<ul>\n<li>vim为编辑器，可自行更改为其它编辑器，但非常建议使用vim。学习vim的操作不会很难，常用的命令只有那么几个，习惯了就好。</li>\n<li>curl可以优化termux终端界面，酌情下载安装。</li>\n<li>clang为C和C++编译器。</li>\n<li>python可以让我们制作一些对拍小程序，也有很多其它的玩法，酌情下载安装。</li>\n<li>gdb和cgdb为调试工具，可根据需要酌情下载安装。</li>\n<li>也可自行安装其它软件及工具。</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"vim的使用\">vim的使用<a title=\"#vim的使用\" href=\"#vim的使用\"></a></h2>\n<p>下面是vim的一些简单命令。</p>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">命令</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">含义</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">vim &lt;文件名&gt;</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">编辑文件，若文件不存在则自动创建新文件</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">i</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">切换到编辑模式</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">ESC</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">退出编辑模式</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">:x</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">保存退出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">:q</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">未改动退出</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">:q!</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">不保存退出</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p>更多命令请自行搜索相关资料。</p>\n<h2 id=\"c++的编译与运行\">C++的编译与运行<a title=\"#c++的编译与运行\" href=\"#c++的编译与运行\"></a></h2>\n<h3 id=\"编译\">编译<a title=\"#编译\" href=\"#编译\"></a></h3>\n<p>切换到cpp文件目录（cd &lt;目录&gt;）后命令如下：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">g++ &lt;cpp代码文件&gt; -o &lt;生成程序名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如：</p>\n<p>g++ hello.cpp -o hello</p>\n<p>即可在该目录下生成名为hello的可执行文件。</p>\n<h3 id=\"运行\">运行<a title=\"#运行\" href=\"#运行\"></a></h3>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">./&lt;可执行文件名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如:</p>\n<p>./hello</p>\n<p>即可执行hello程序。</p>\n<p>如出现错误：permission denied</p>\n<p>则说明没有权限访问该程序，此时输入：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">chmod +x &lt;程序名&gt;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>如：</p>\n<p>chmod +x hello</p>\n<p>即可执行。</p>\n<h2 id=\"可选步骤\">可选步骤<a title=\"#可选步骤\" href=\"#可选步骤\"></a></h2>\n<p>以下为可选步骤，但非常建议做一做。</p>\n<h3 id=\"创建工作目录\">创建工作目录<a title=\"#创建工作目录\" href=\"#创建工作目录\"></a></h3>\n<p>建议在根目录中新建一个文件夹作为工作目录，如果你比较懒，之后直接在根目录中编辑文件也是可以的。</p>\n<p>名字建议用纯英文字母，方便进入。</p>\n<p>建议不使用会与命令起冲突的名字，比如gcc，cpp。</p>\n<h3 id=\"配置vim\">配置vim<a title=\"#配置vim\" href=\"#配置vim\"></a></h3>\n<p>其实可以不配置，但是非常建议配置。</p>\n<p>配置之后会给打代码增添不少便利。</p>\n<p>执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim ~/.vimrc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>将以下内容复制粘贴进去保存即可。</p>\n<p>可根据需要自行修改。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br><span class=\"line\">96</span><br><span class=\"line\">97</span><br><span class=\"line\">98</span><br><span class=\"line\">99</span><br><span class=\"line\">100</span><br><span class=\"line\">101</span><br><span class=\"line\">102</span><br><span class=\"line\">103</span><br><span class=\"line\">104</span><br><span class=\"line\">105</span><br><span class=\"line\">106</span><br><span class=\"line\">107</span><br><span class=\"line\">108</span><br><span class=\"line\">109</span><br><span class=\"line\">110</span><br><span class=\"line\">111</span><br><span class=\"line\">112</span><br><span class=\"line\">113</span><br><span class=\"line\">114</span><br><span class=\"line\">115</span><br><span class=\"line\">116</span><br><span class=\"line\">117</span><br><span class=\"line\">118</span><br><span class=\"line\">119</span><br><span class=\"line\">120</span><br><span class=\"line\">121</span><br><span class=\"line\">122</span><br><span class=\"line\">123</span><br><span class=\"line\">124</span><br><span class=\"line\">125</span><br><span class=\"line\">126</span><br><span class=\"line\">127</span><br><span class=\"line\">128</span><br><span class=\"line\">129</span><br><span class=\"line\">130</span><br><span class=\"line\">131</span><br><span class=\"line\">132</span><br><span class=\"line\">133</span><br><span class=\"line\">134</span><br><span class=\"line\">135</span><br><span class=\"line\">136</span><br><span class=\"line\">137</span><br><span class=\"line\">138</span><br><span class=\"line\">139</span><br><span class=\"line\">140</span><br><span class=\"line\">141</span><br><span class=\"line\">142</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">&quot; 设置当文件被改动时自动载入&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set autoread</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; quickfix模式&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">autocmd FileType c,cpp map &lt;buffer&gt; &lt;leader&gt;&lt;space&gt; :w&lt;cr&gt;:make&lt;cr&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;代码补全 &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set completeopt=preview,menu </span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;允许插件  &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype plugin on</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;共享剪贴板  &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set clipboard=unnamed </span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;从不备份  &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set nobackup</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;自动保存&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set autowrite</span><br><span class=\"line\">set ruler  &quot; 打开状态栏标尺&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set cursorline  &quot;突出显示当前行&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set magic  &quot; 设置魔术&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set guioptions-=T  &quot;隐藏工具栏&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set guioptions-=m  &quot;隐藏菜单栏&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set foldcolumn=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">set foldmethod=indent </span><br><span class=\"line\">set foldlevel=3 </span><br><span class=\"line\">set foldenable  &quot; 开始折叠&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 不要使用vi的键盘模式，而是vim自己的&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set nocompatible</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 语法高亮&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set syntax=on</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 去掉输入错误的提示声音&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set noeb</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 在处理未保存或只读文件的时候，弹出确认&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set confirm</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;自动缩进 &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set autoindent</span><br><span class=\"line\">set cindent</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; Tab键的宽度&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set tabstop=4</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 统一缩进为4&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set softtabstop=4</span><br><span class=\"line\">set shiftwidth=4</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 不要用空格代替制表符&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set noexpandtab</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 在行和段开始处使用制表符&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set smarttab</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 显示行号&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set number</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 历史记录数&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set history=1000</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;禁止生成临时文件&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set nobackup</span><br><span class=\"line\">set noswapfile</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;搜索忽略大小写&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set ignorecase</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;搜索逐字符高亮&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set hlsearch</span><br><span class=\"line\">set incsearch</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;行内替换&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set gdefault</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;编码设置&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set enc=utf-8</span><br><span class=\"line\">set fencs=utf-8,ucs-bom,shift-jis,gb18030,gbk,gb2312,cp936</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;语言设置&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set langmenu=zh_CN.UTF-8</span><br><span class=\"line\">set helplang=cn</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 我的状态行显示的内容（包括文件类型和解码）&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set statusline=[%F]%y%r%m%*%=[Line:%l/%L,Column:%c][%p%%]</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 总是显示状态行&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set laststatus=2</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 命令行（在状态行下）的高度，默认为1，这里是2&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set cmdheight=2</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 侦测文件类型&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype on</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 载入文件类型插件&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype plugin on</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 为特定文件类型载入相关缩进文件&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype indent on</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 保存全局变量&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set viminfo+=!</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 带有如下符号的单词不要被换行分割&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set iskeyword+=_,$,@,%,#,-</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 字符间插入的像素行数目&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set linespace=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 增强模式中的命令行自动完成操作&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set wildmenu</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 使回格键（backspace）正常处理indent, eol, start等&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set backspace=2</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 允许backspace和光标键跨越行边界&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set whichwrap+=&lt;,&gt;,h,l</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 可以在buffer的任何地方使用鼠标（类似office中在工作区双击鼠标定位）&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set mouse=a</span><br><span class=\"line\">set selection=exclusive</span><br><span class=\"line\">set selectmode=mouse,key</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 通过使用: commands命令，告诉我们文件的哪一行被改变过&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set report=0</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 高亮显示匹配的括号&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set showmatch</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 匹配括号高亮的时间（单位是十分之一秒）&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set matchtime=1</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 光标移动到buffer的顶部和底部时保持3行距离&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set scrolloff=3</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 为C程序提供自动缩进&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set smartindent</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot; 高亮显示普通txt文件（需要txt.vim脚本）&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\"> au BufRead,BufNewFile *  setfiletype txt</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;自动补全&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap ( ()&lt;ESC&gt;i</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap ) &lt;c-r&gt;=ClosePair(&#x27;)&#x27;)&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap &#123; &#123;&lt;CR&gt;&#125;&lt;ESC&gt;O</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap &#125; &lt;c-r&gt;=ClosePair(&#x27;&#125;&#x27;)&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap [ []&lt;ESC&gt;i</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap ] &lt;c-r&gt;=ClosePair(&#x27;]&#x27;)&lt;CR&gt;</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap &quot; &quot;&quot;&lt;ESC&gt;i</span><br><span class=\"line\">:inoremap &#x27; &#x27;&#x27;&lt;ESC&gt;i</span><br><span class=\"line\">function! ClosePair(char)</span><br><span class=\"line\">    if getline(&#x27;.&#x27;)[col(&#x27;.&#x27;) - 1] == a:char</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return &quot;/&lt;Right&gt;&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    else</span><br><span class=\"line\">        return a:char</span><br><span class=\"line\">    endif</span><br><span class=\"line\">endfunction</span><br><span class=\"line\">filetype plugin indent on </span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;打开文件类型检测, 加了这句才可以用智能补全&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">set completeopt=longest,menu</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;C++的编译和运行  &quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;编译运行&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">map &lt;F10&gt; :call CompileRunGpp()&lt;CR&gt;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">func! CompileRunGpp()  </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;w&quot;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;!g++ % -o %&lt;&quot;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;! ./%&lt;&quot;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">endfunc</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;编译&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">map &lt;F8&gt; :call CompileGpp()&lt;cr&gt;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">func! CompileGpp()  </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;w&quot;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;!g++ % -o %&lt;&quot;  </span><br><span class=\"line\">endfunc</span><br><span class=\"line\">&quot;运行&quot;</span><br><span class=\"line\">map &lt;F9&gt; :call RunGpp()&lt;cr&gt;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">func! RunGpp()    </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;w&quot;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">exec &quot;! ./%&lt;&quot;    </span><br><span class=\"line\">endfunc</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存后再次进入一个cpp文件时，编辑将会更加方便，并可以在vim编辑器中直接编译和运行。</p>\n<h4 id=\"操作方法\">操作方法<a title=\"#操作方法\" href=\"#操作方法\"></a></h4>\n<div class=\"φbq\"><div class=\"φbs\"><table><thead>\n<tr>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">按键</th>\n<th style=\"text-align:center\">作用</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">F8（音量+键+ 8）</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">编译</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">F9（音量+键 + 9）</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">运行</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">F10（音量+键 + 0）</td>\n<td style=\"text-align:center\">编译并运行</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table></div></div><p>当然，也可以模仿上面的代码创造自己的快捷键，比如gdb调试。</p>\n<h3 id=\"优化termux终端界面\">优化termux终端界面<a title=\"#优化termux终端界面\" href=\"#优化termux终端界面\"></a></h3>\n<p>使用zsh来替代bash作为默认shell。</p>\n<p>在已安装curl的情况下使用以下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">sh -c &quot;$(curl -fsSL https://github.com/Cabbagec/termux-ohmyzsh/raw/master/install.sh)&quot;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>Android 6.0以上可能会弹框确认是否授权访问文件，点击允许，之后会在termux根目录生成storage目录，可以方便地对外部文件进行操作。</p>\n<p>安装成功后先后会有两个选项，分别选择背景色和字体，如下：</p>\n<p>Enter a number, leave blank to not to change:</p>\n<p>Enter a number, leave blank to not to change:</p>\n<p>我选的是14和6，仅供参考。</p>\n<p>如果希望再次更改配色，可执行如下命令：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">~/termux-ohmyzsh/install.sh</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>重启软件或开启新session生效。</p>\n<h3 id=\"修改启动问候语\">修改启动问候语<a title=\"#修改启动问候语\" href=\"#修改启动问候语\"></a></h3>\n<p>可以编辑问候语文件直接修改问候语。</p>\n<p>输入如下命令即可修改：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">vim $PREFIX/etc/motd</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>保存重启即可。</p>\n<h2 id=\"termux的其他玩法\">termux的其他玩法<a title=\"#termux的其他玩法\" href=\"#termux的其他玩法\"></a></h2>\n<ul>\n<li>termux可以在手机上安装正规linux，比如ubuntu、kali，并能安装桌面（也就是说可以图形化操作）， 但NOI linux除外（大雾） ；</li>\n<li>termux可以愉快地玩耍python，制作网络爬虫、微信机器人以及其它；</li>\n<li>在termux上安装kali-linux及其它安全工具，靠自己来暴力破解WIFI， 并从此走上CTF的不归路（大雾） ；</li>\n<li>在termux上运用php和WordPress或hexo搭建网站和博客；</li>\n<li>用termux ssh远程连接电脑，从此躺在床上就可以操作电脑；</li>\n<li>在termux上使用Aria2打造自己的下载工具，配置好的话还可以高速下载百度云文件；</li>\n<li>安装Termux-api，直接操作调动系统底层，用代码发短信、打电话。</li>\n</ul>\n<hr>\n<p>termux作为一个linux模拟器，可实现的功能远远不止打打C++和python的代码，希望有更多的人能够认识termux的强大并挖掘出更多玩法，也希望能够有更多关于termux的优秀文章出现。</p>\n<h2 id=\"文章部分内容引用地址\">文章部分内容引用地址<a title=\"#文章部分内容引用地址\" href=\"#文章部分内容引用地址\"></a></h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.sqlsec.com/2018/05/termux.html\" target=\"_blank\">Termux 高级终端安装使用配置教程 - 国光</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.cnblogs.com/jokerBi/articles/10609264.html\" target=\"_blank\">vim美化基本配置</a></p>\n<p>头图来源：国光博客头图</p>\n<h2 id=\"推荐阅读\">推荐阅读<a title=\"#推荐阅读\" href=\"#推荐阅读\"></a></h2>\n<p>知乎专栏：<a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/c_1208079877376901120\" target=\"_blank\">安卓手机配合linux新玩法挖掘</a></p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p>…</p>\n<p>彩蛋：</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight plaintext\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\">pkg install nyancat</span><br><span class=\"line\">nyancat</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n","prev":{"title":"清理电脑C盘简要攻略","link":"post/cleancomputer"},"plink":"https://jwjawa.js.org/blog/post/termuxandcpp/","toc":[{"id":"下载安装termux","title":"下载安装termux","index":"1"},{"id":"更换国内镜像源","title":"更换国内镜像源","index":"2"},{"id":"linux基础命令","title":"linux基础命令","index":"3"},{"id":"安装软件及工具","title":"安装软件及工具","index":"4"},{"id":"vim的使用","title":"vim的使用","index":"5"},{"id":"c++的编译与运行","title":"C++的编译与运行","index":"6","children":[{"id":"编译","title":"编译","index":"6.1"},{"id":"运行","title":"运行","index":"6.2"}]},{"id":"可选步骤","title":"可选步骤","index":"7","children":[{"id":"创建工作目录","title":"创建工作目录","index":"7.1"},{"id":"配置vim","title":"配置vim","index":"7.2"},{"id":"优化termux终端界面","title":"优化termux终端界面","index":"7.3"},{"id":"修改启动问候语","title":"修改启动问候语","index":"7.4"}]},{"id":"termux的其他玩法","title":"termux的其他玩法","index":"8"},{"id":"文章部分内容引用地址","title":"文章部分内容引用地址","index":"9"},{"id":"推荐阅读","title":"推荐阅读","index":"10"}],"reading_time":"2629 字约 18 分钟"}